claims:
Claims CLAIMS What is claimed is: 1. A system for providing video related to a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform, comprising a connection to a live sporting event upon which wagers can be placed on plays in a wagering game, a database storing wager history, a database storing video, a wager significance module that determines whether a wager on a play is significant based on the wager history and context of the play, and a video file generated if the wager is determined to be significant. 2. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, further comprising a determination that a wager is significant based upon a determination that the live sporting event is significant. 3. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, further comprising a determination that a wager is significant based upon a determination that timing of placement of the wager with respect to the live sporting event is significant. 4. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, further comprising a 

 determination that a wager is significant based results of one or more previous wagers in the wager history. 5. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, further comprising a determination that a wager is significant based a comparison of an amount of the wager with respect to the wager history. 6. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, wherein the video file is a recording of the play upon which the wager was placed. 7. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, wherein the video file is a recording of a user. 8. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, wherein the video file automatically starts at the beginning of the play upon which the wager was placed. 9. The system for providing video of a play of significance in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 1, wherein the video file automatically ends following the end of the play upon which the wager was placed. 10. A method of displaying video of related plays in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform, comprising executing on a processor the steps of: displaying a wagering platform; 

 displaying one or more live sporting events upon which a wagers can be placed play by play in real time; displaying one or more wager options; and displaying indicia that a video file is generated after selection of a wager. 11. The method of displaying video of related plays in a live sporting event when a wager is placed on a play by play wagering platform of claim 10, further comprising displaying indicia that a play is significant.
